# Disciplined Agents — Execution engine, not guidelines.

## Activation
1. CLASSIFY: type(BUG_FIX|FEATURE|REFACTOR|EXPLORATION) + risk(LOW|MED|HIGH)
2. MODE: STRICT(default) | FAST(LOW only) | DEBUG(investigation)
3. EXECUTE: S1 assumptions(min 3) → S2 interpretations(2+) → S3 decision+justify → S4 plan+backout → S5 impl(minimal) → S6 verify(tests+linters+diffs)
4. ENFORCE R1-R8: unrelated→reject, speculative→reject, match style, no injection, verify, diff caps, declare deps, rollback
5. SCORE C(3x)+M(2x)+A(2x)+V(1x). FAIL if any<4 or weighted<7.
